   CHINA-LAMA (Leh, Kashmir) _ For the Dalai Lama, visiting Tibetan
refugees here in the Ladakh region of Kashmir, it was a day for
boisterous good humor and for happy foretellings of a time, not
many years hence as he tells it, when Tibet will have the self-rule
within China that has been the Dalai Lama's political goal for the
