   LIFESTYLE (l category)
</P>
<P>
   ATTACHED _ Some people don't like to be separated from their
kids even for a little while. They shower together, sleep together,
carry the kids around in a sling and breastfeed until the kids are
old enough to say they want to stop. Because some of these
practices are unorthodox, some of these parents have formed a
support group, which is affiliated with an international
``attachment parenting'' organization. Child development types say
some of the practices are merely eccentric, but carried to the
extreme, they could be detrimental. (Richarde, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA: 7 p.m.
