</P>
<P>
   It's true. Women and men are not created equal. Women can do
many things better.
</P>
<P>
   .........OO..OO..OO..OO..OO..OO..OO.........
</P>
<P>
   ......OO...OO...OO...OO...OO...OO...OO......
