<SLUG> BC-TV-BAYWATCH-450&AMP;ADD-SFCHRON </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
`BAYWATCH' WANNABES TAKE THE BUOYANCY TEST 
</HEADLINE>
   (Eds: This story also moved in the ``l'' lifestyle news file)  
 By JOHN CARMAN  
 c.1998, San Francisco Chronicle  
<TEXT>
<P>
