<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   IRELAND-ANALYSIS (Belfast) -- When the new Northern Ireland
Assembly holds its inaugural meeting on Wednesday in the same room
where the agreement that created it was reached, the fights will
begin immediately. By Kevin Cullen. 1300 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   OLIPHANT-COLUMN (Washington) _ Even in house detention Zhao
Ziyang has never quite shut up, as was apparent when a letter he
wrote his former comrades in the Chinese leadership surfaced. By
