pennant winners are built around pitching and defense _ and the law
finally won this season. The M's are built around power and marquee
players but lack the subleties that produce consistent winners. The
team has defensive liabilities in three spots (second, third, left
field), lacks speed and miscalculated when it opened this season
with virtually that same bullpen as last year.
</P>
