<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-KOSOVO-ART-725&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
SERBIANS UNLEASH SERIES OF HEAVY ATTACKS AGAINST ALBANIAN
SEPARATISTS 
</HEADLINE>
  (ART ADV.: a map locating Belacevac is being sent to NYT graphics
clients. Non-subscribers may make individual purchase by calling
212 556-4204.) 
(ps) 
 By CHRIS HEDGES   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
