  (th) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   GTE Corp., Stamford, Conn., named Daniel O'Brien chief financial
officer and executive vice president for finance, succeeding J.
Michael Kelly, who resigned to become chief financial officer at
America Online Inc. O'Brien had been GTE's vice president and
treasurer.
</P>
