Limited clothing store chains, named Robin Burns president of its
Limited New Ventures Inc. division. She will report to the chairman
and chief executive, Leslie Wexner, about projects aimed at
expanding the retailer of women's and men's clothing. Ms. Burns was
formerly president and chief executive of Estee Lauder's operations
in the United States and Canada. &QL;
